<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad Schütz</head><p>Der Rat gewährt dem Adressaten bis Obersten Tag zwei Tage Geleit wegen Heinrich Reck, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_218" id="108r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_218_r2l15">. C . Schücʒen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l16"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Conrad Als Jr vns
                                <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l17">habt von <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Recken
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> wegen etc / Das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l18">vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / Vnd alſo
                        vvenn Jr <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l19">Oberſten ſchierſt darümb herein kumt / So ſüllt Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l20">vnd die mit euch alſo herein kumen cʒwen tag bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l21">geleyt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> on
                                <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> Vnd ſo
                            <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr
                        rede </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_218_r2l22"><expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> hören /
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>vig<ex>ilia</ex></expan>
<expan>Nati<ex>uita</ex><hi rend="sup">t<ex>is</ex></hi></expan>xpi</ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_218" id="108r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>C<ex>onrad</ex> Schüczen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Conrad, als ir uns
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
                        habt von Heinr<ex>ich</ex> Recken <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> wegen etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>.
                        Und also wenn ir <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app>
<note><q type="date">obersten schierst</q>06.01.1421</note>
</app> darümb herein kumt, so süllt ir und die mit euch also herein kumen
                        czwen tag bey uns geleyt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> on
                                <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan> und so
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr rede
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> hören. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        in <expan>vig<ex>ilia</ex></expan>
<expan>nati<ex>vita</ex><hi rend="sup">t<ex>is</ex>
</hi></expan> Christi.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
